Âµe - an ANSI tty micro text editor by grunfink - public domain

goals:

* stripped, size-optimized size of amd64 object (NOT executable) < 5K
* copy/paste
* expects an utf-8 environment (both ANSI terminal and documents)
* 1 file
* no syntax highlight
* no undo

keys:

ctrl-a  beginning of line
ctrl-b  mark selection
ctrl-c  copy to clipboard
ctrl-d  delete char
ctrl-e  end of line
ctrl-h  move left
ctrl-j  move down
ctrl-k  move up
ctrl-l  move right
ctrl-n  next page
ctrl-p  previous page
ctrl-q  quit
ctrl-s  save document
ctrl-u  unmark selection
ctrl-v  paste from clipboard
ctrl-x  cut to clipboard
ctrl-y  delete line
